title: Borders Store Locations 12.2007
name: Borders Store Locations 12.2007
description:
Borders Group is an international bookseller based in Ann Arbor, Michigan. Started in 1960 by two brothers attending the University of Michigan the company has grown to be the second-largest bookstore chain in the United States. The Borders Group consists of Borders, Borders Express, Borders Outlet, and Waldenbooks. The stores sell a wide variety of books, CDs, DVDs, periodicals, and other gifts.

This dataset displays all of the Borders locations across the United States and in Puerto Rico. The dataset contains the store's full physical address, phone, and lat/lon coordinates. Addresses were obtained from borders.com and are current as of 12.2007. Addresses were geocoded to obtain their lat/lon coordinates.

For more information, go to borders.com
